# Restaurant Data Analysis Dashboard

This Power BI project showcases an interactive dashboard designed to analyze key performance metrics for a restaurant business. It provides insights into daily sales, customer behavior, product performance, and revenue trends.

## 🔍 Features

- Sales breakdown by item, category, and date
- Daily, weekly, and monthly performance trends
- Top-selling and low-performing menu items
- Customer footfall and order frequency patterns
- Visualizations using bar charts, pie charts, cards, and slicers
- Built with Power Query, Data Modeling, and DAX

## 📊 Tools Used

- Microsoft Power BI (Desktop)
- Power Query
- DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)

## 📁 File

- `Restaurant Data Analysis Dashboard.pbix` – Power BI Dashboard file

## 💡 Use Case

This dashboard can be used by restaurant managers and owners to:
- Monitor sales trends and customer preferences
- Optimize menu offerings
- Improve operational efficiency based on peak hours and demand

## 🚀 Getting Started

1. Download or clone this repository
2. Open the `.pbix` file using Power BI Desktop
3. Explore the dashboard and customize it as needed

---

Feel free to fork this project or use it as a reference for your own data analysis work.
